<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Kimigayo</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Kimigayo, or &quot;His Imperial Majesty's Reign&quot;, is the national anthem of Japan. With its lyrics based from a waka poem dating back to the Heian period, it is one of the oldest and shortest national anthems in current use.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="h8x2ty">
